      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been such a reliable ride for me and is still in really solid shape! It runs great, looks lovely, and has plenty of life left in it for all your adventures. I\u2019ve taken good care of it, so you\u2019re getting a fantastic vehicle that\u2019s ready to hit the road today. Feel free to ask any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound 2008 Porsche Cayman S, a mid-engine platform optimized for technical driving. This specimen features the M97 3.4L naturally aspirated flat-six, mated to a precise 6-speed manual transaxle. The vehicle is equipped with Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM), providing adaptive damping that remains sharp and responsive. Recent preventative maintenance includes a cooling system overhaul with a new water pump and low-temp thermostat, alongside a fresh set of staggered Michelin Pilot Sport 4S tires. The braking system utilizes four-piston monoblock calipers with plenty of pad life remaining. While the exterior shows honest road wear consistent with its mileage, the drivetrain remains tight with no signs of bore scoring or IMS weeping. This is a driver-spec 987 with excellent turn-in and balanced polar inertia, ready for the enthusiast who values longitudinal and lateral performance over a showroom-queen status.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
