    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a dependable, high-quality driver. The exterior is finished in a timeless coat that still holds a high-gloss shine, though there are minor, age-appropriate stone chips on the hood and a small hairline scratch near the trunk lid that do not detract from its overall presence. Inside, the cabin has been smoke-free and well-preserved; the upholstery is intact with only light creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster, and the carpets have been protected by floor mats since day one. Every button, dial, and digital display functions perfectly, including the premium audio system and dual-zone climate control. Under the hood, the car is mechanically sound with a complete service log. It has recently undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection, receiving a fresh oil change and new brake pads. The tires have significant tread depth remaining, and the alloy wheels are free of major curb rash. This is a turn-key car that drives straight, shifts smoothly, and offers a refined experience on the road.",
